These files should be installed under data/add-ons/Trogdor_The_Burninator, to replace the files of the same name in Glubul's Saga, as well as all the similarly
named files in 2.4.2026 R Trogdor start.
See Wesnoth site about how to access add-ons: https://wiki.wesnoth.org/AddonStructure
These files are based on the add-on Glubul's Saga, by Argesilao.
Changes made so far include new map, which has been integrated into the scenarios, some file name changes, deletions from the scenarios, deletions from
units, working but buggy terrain change function, and implemented human enemy side. 
